            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">et re</supplied>ditu et <expan><abbr>vict</abbr><ex>oria</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">He</supplied>rmes <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">signum cu</supplied>m <expan><abbr>stat</abbr><ex>era</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>ponder</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">coloniae</supplied> <expan><abbr>Mint</abbr><ex>urnensium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ono</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Dreieckige Interpunktionen. (B): Z. 3/4: Cavuoto, AE: [--- He]rmes Aug(usti) / [servus? - libertus?] stat(eram) et ponder(a).</p>
